These combine into a single operator field:

\Pi(t) = B(t)\;R(t)\;V_L(t)

Where:
	‚Ä¢	B(t) = cognitive bandwidth
	‚Ä¢	R(t) = ethical / structural alignment rails
	‚Ä¢	V_L(t) = luck vector (direction + magnitude)

This Synthesis Engine explains why a calm, ethically aligned, momentum-rich operator appears ‚Äúsupernaturally lucky.‚Äù
It is a mechanistic, not mystical, model.

